OL,3,CPolice murder probe as man dies after
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation following the death of a
OL,8,Fman in north Belfast.
OL,10,FPaul Mackin Jr, 44, died from his
OL,11,Finjuries on Wednesday evening after an
OL,12,Fattack in house on Duncairn Parade on
OL,13,FMonday.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Jenni Rea
OL,16,Fsaid: "Just before 6pm on Monday, 20th
OL,17,FJuly, we received a report of an
OL,18,Fassault at a residential property in
OL,19,Fthe Duncairn Parade area.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
