OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784823526
OL,3,CPolice murder probe as man dies after
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"Officers attended the scene alongside
OL,7,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,8,FAmbulance Service. A 44-year-old man
OL,9,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment.
OL,10,F"Three men ` aged 40, 41 and 32 ` were
OL,11,Farrested a short time later on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of attempted murder.
OL,14,F"Sadly, the injured man, Paul Mackin
OL,15,FJunior from the north Belfast area,
OL,16,Fpassed away in hospital yesterday
OL,17,Fevening, Wednesday 22nd July.
OL,19,F"The arrested 41-year-old man has now
OL,20,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
