PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784823526
OL,3,CPolice murder probe as man dies after
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"The 32-year-old man has been released
OL,7,Funconditionally."
OL,9,FDetective Chief Inspector Rea added:
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are with Paul's family
OL,11,Fat this incredibly difficult time.
OL,13,F"Police would ask that the public
OL,14,Favoid speculation on the circumstances
OL,15,Faround this matter, which is upsetting
OL,16,Ffor the family and friends of Mr
OL,17,FMackin, and could have a detrimental
OL,18,Fimpact on criminal justice proceedings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@QO]rD@AOUuD@AOU
